<p>Any design isn't fully finished without its details. Country interiors are curated through time, as generation after generation have passed down their most prized possessions. Along with antique furnishings and vintage accoutrements, accessories add an extra touch that brings the design together. Nature inspired collections, farm life adornments, and general primitive additions are all found in country interiors. However it is crucial to keep a tight-rein on these as too many or too much begins to make the design feel kitschy and ungenuine. </p>
